<item>
            <title>[LU-10107] Truncate doesn&apos;t work at component boundary</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10107</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Truncate doesn&apos;t work at component boundary with the next component uninstantiated. The root cause is that the previous implement only sends truncate RPC to components overlapping with [size, eof), where it should be [size - 1, eof).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
